'''2018年二十國集團布宜諾斯艾利斯峰會'''（{{lang-en|2018 G20 Buenos Aires summit}}），是[[二十國集團|二十國集團]]第十三次高峰會，於2018年11月30日至12月1日在[[阿根廷|阿根廷]][[布宜諾斯艾利斯|布宜諾斯艾利斯]]舉行<ref>{{cite web|title=Argentina fue elegida sede del G-20 para 2018|publisher=clarin|url=http://www.clarin.com/politica/Argentina-elegida-sede-G-20_0_1603039808.html|date=2016-06-28|author=Natasha Niebieskikwiat|accessdate=2016-07-31|language=en|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628140647/http://www.clarin.com/politica/Argentina-elegida-sede-G-20_0_1603039808.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。但申辦[[2019年二十國集團峰會|2019年]]的國家當中，[[印度|印度]]曾提出更改為2018年主辦的要求，表示會遇到[[印度總理|印度總理]]選舉日期，並計畫在[[新德里|新德里]]舉行<ref>{{cite web|title=India to hold G20 Chair in 2018, Delhi may play host|publisher=The Hindu|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/india-to-hold-g20-chair-in-2018-delhi-may-play-host/article7708086.ece|date=2015-10-01|author=Puja Mehra|accessdate=2016-07-31|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108094327/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/india-to-hold-g20-chair-in-2018-delhi-may-play-host/article7708086.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=India pitches to host G20 meet before turn|publisher=Economic Times|url=http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/policy/india-pitches-to-host-g20-meet-before-turn/articleshow/53145866.cms|date=2016-05-01|author=Deepshikha Sikarwar|accessdate=2016-07-31|language=en|archive-date=2019-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191028220000/https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/economy/policy/india-pitches-to-host-g20-meet-before-turn/articleshow/53145866.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=India proposes to host G20 summit ahead of schedule To undertake the responsibility without distractions|publisher=Media India Group|url=http://mediaindia.eu/business-politics/india-proposes-to-host-g20-summit-ahead-of-schedule/|date=2016-07-18|author=Arachika Kapoor|accessdate=2016-07-31|language=en|archive-date